{"tid":775282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【吐黑水死亡】英UFO專家波蘭離奇猝死 電腦資料被刪除無法確定死因","createTime":"2018-08-11T04:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T05:18:55.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d138533e44f8a1a678d6655d94e3eb8f82ac530d","tid":775282,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:59:05.000Z","msg":"【更新內容】<br />\n<br />\n英國一名陰謀論家到波蘭開會時，突然吐出兩公升黑色液體死亡，英國醫院表示無法確定其死因，波蘭當局卻指他「死於自然」，又把他的手提電腦內的資料全部刪除才交還其家人。死者家人現唯有等英國調查報告，追查死因。<br />\n39歲的施皮爾斯(Max Spiers)是一名不明飛行物體專家，他兩年前前往波蘭出席一個會議，但突然吐出兩公升黑色液體後死亡，手提電腦資料全部被清除。施皮爾斯離奇死亡前，曾發短訊給母親說：「兒子有麻煩了，若我有不測，調查。」想不到真的出事。<br />\n英國當局原於2016年12月召開死因庭，但去年聆訊擱置，暫定明年1月重開。施皮爾斯是兩子之父，因其調查工作，樹敵不少。代表施皮爾斯母親的律師說，施皮爾斯死時電腦載有資料，但其家人取回電腦時，所有資料都被刪掉，令事件倍添疑團。由於急救記錄對施皮爾斯之死有不少不吻合之處，律師希望傳召波蘭的急救人員前來作供，但未知能否成事。<br />\n律師又證實有關施皮爾斯手提電腦和手機的分析報告將呈堂，其中其手機SIM卡的資料可能是關鍵。<br />\n施皮爾斯遺體送回英國後，英國的醫生表示無法確定他的死因。他媽媽表示，施皮爾斯前往波蘭前的身體報告都顯示健康良好。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180811/58549762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180811%2F58549762&d=Oduy08sX6Lr3Yv6xxZYNfU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=7555a163\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180811%2F58549762&h=e8a39c96\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180811/58549762</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180811/large/1533943190_71c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180811%2Flarge%2F1533943190_71c7.jpg&h=8bd39424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n施皮爾斯死因神秘(互聯網)"},{"pid":"0c2577e001cb1a3c5a392a86624f2cbf6137e15d","tid":775282,"uid":59030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:00:45.000Z","msg":"普羅咪收屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2675f92764f60532235c51cb7309248cc16f7ad4","tid":775282,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2fd923f478ecfc897170c1ce310750f5dd46331","tid":775282,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"咩來"},{"pid":"6a207cb304a3e8dd4d33335b56a9e52432338da8","tid":775282,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:08:24.000Z","msg":"x file<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc9a509762b44fd7f77cfc9a7144394a1d61c03","tid":775282,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f6476834659106f726dd8a696b6790d4a17261","tid":775282,"uid":7877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8200480cbaf11bc100585fc2b953ee6ad010ec41","tid":775282,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"波蘭狗 擺買cyberpunk2077"},{"pid":"a977ba385d2b50703fc76aa421b36b233a68838c","tid":775282,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:11:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波蘭狗 罷買cyberpunk2077--</blockquote>"},{"pid":"742787f086b57fc5cf0e767499e1d110519ccca4","tid":775282,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 